9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Orb: On the Movements of the Earth | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The setting is 15th-century Europe. It was a time when heretical ideas lead those to who possessed such a mindset to being burned at the stake for their beliefs.<br><br>\n\nThe protagonist, Rafał, a child prodigy, is expected to major in theology, the most important subject at the time, at the university where he plans to skip a grade. One day, however, he comes across a mysterious man, and is now studying a possible \"truth\" in the midst of heretical thought!<br><br>\n(Source: Shogakukan, translated)"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149702/orb-on-the-movements-of-the-earth"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Orb: On the Movements of the Earth"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"The setting is 15th-century Europe. It was a time when heretical ideas lead those to who possessed such a mindset to being burned at the stake for their beliefs.<br><br>\n\nThe protagonist, Rafał, a child prodigy, is expected to major in theology, the most important subject at the time, at the university where he plans to skip a grade. One day, however, he comes across a mysterious man, and is now studying a possible \"truth\" in the midst of heretical thought!<br><br>\n(Source: Shogakukan, translated)"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/series/149702/orb-on-the-movements-of-the-earth"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx151514-Y0d82Ah2ZOHX.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.tv_show"}],["$","meta